# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REAL ESTATE DATA — MUST NEVER BE COMMITTED
#
# The only files that belong in this repo are the schema, the
# example (dummy data), the templates, and the scripts. Your
# real register is private and lives outside version control.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# The live register (plaintext), wherever it sits in the tree
estate.yaml
estate.yml

# Any encrypted register. The .age file should live outside the
# repo anyway; this is belt-and-braces in case one is created here.
# The .sha256 sidecar only hashes ciphertext, but it still describes
# a private file — keep it out too.
*.age
*.age.sha256

# Passphrase shares must never be written to disk at all — but if
# someone redirects ssss output to a file, don't let git pick it up.
*share*.txt
*.shares

# Derived from the private register (render.sh / make-guide.sh /
# review.sh / test-recovery.sh outputs) — as private as the register.
executor-report.md
executor-report.html
EXECUTOR-INSTRUCTIONS-filled.md
EXECUTOR-INSTRUCTIONS-filled.html
executor-file-reminders.ics
recovery-tests.log

# OS noise
.DS_Store
